# Test API endpoints locally (use with REST Client extension)

### Get all artists
GET http://localhost:3000/artists

### Get artist by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/artist/123

### Get artists by styles
GET http://localhost:3000/artists/Tribal,Old%20School

### Update artist
PATCH http://localhost:3000/artist/123
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "artistsName": "Updated Name",
  "bio": "Updated bio"
}

### Submit removal request
POST http://localhost:3000/removal-requests
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "instagramHandle": "test_artist",
  "reason": "Privacy request"
}